	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas, quas ad me misisti Tiguro, ornatissime <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>, porro transmittendas ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p380" cert="high">Ioannem Bircmannum</persName> scriptas 20. augusti, receptas in sequenti die <placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Francfordiam</placeName> ad eundem perferri curavi, tardius autem ad me, nempe 8. septembris allate sunt.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Circiter eosdem dies unas ad magnificentiam tuam dedi, in quibus, quantum per febriles infestationes licuit, et de rebus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxonicis</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglicis</placeName> cognita tibi communicavi, postea quoque omnem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglię</placeName> statum vel verius conflictationes <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p506" cert="high">Ioanni Butlero</persName> Anglo apud vos commoranti adscripsimus, ut is tue magnificentie ac aliis optimis quibusque viris super eventu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglicarum</placeName> tumultuationum sollicitis magis commodam quam expetendam serenissime <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglie</placeName> regis adversum rebelles et tumultuatores victoriam significet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Medio quoque tempore accepimus et alteros illos impia confęderatione pro veteri superstitione revocanda coniuratos dignas sacrilegę rebellionis pęnas dedisse, nempe ad tria milia in pręlio cęsa, reliquam multitudinem effuse fugientem non pertinatius neque longius impetitam esse, concitatores vero et ignarę plebis seductores magna ultione et conquisitione ad supplicia extrahi.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scotia</placeName> tanta omnium rerum penuria est et tanta <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallici</placeName> militis libido et cupido in eos, quos tueri debebant, ut <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scotię</placeName> populus plus commiserationis et integritatis ab hostibus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglis</placeName> quam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallis</placeName> sociis se exoraturum confidat adeoque <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglorum</placeName> adventum magis expetat quam reformidet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallicis</placeName> conatibus ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2122" cert="high">Bulloniam</placeName> cum nihil certi ab amicis acceperim, vos utpote <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallis</placeName> consociatos et coniunctos et eius belli consortes rogatos velim, ut me certiorem facere velitis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui tamen inter tam dissimiles persuasiones et in religione studia, immo contra vos pręiuditia et vobiscum in religione sentientes sancita supplicia constans probitatis et fidei, quę in omnibus humanis actionibus fundamentum est, existimatio esse possit, non video.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego omnia mea offitia magnificentię tuę defero; ut meo nomine salutes <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p506">Butlerum</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1428" cert="high">Christophorum Alesium</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglos</placeName> modo apud vos agentes, rogo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Optime valeas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinae</placeName>, 27. septembris anno 1549.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8121" cert="high">Christophorus Mont</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
